summary:
- **Drilling Delay**: Commencement of drilling at Cobungra CST Prospect (gold-silver) delayed due to rig unavailability; no availability for several weeks.  
- **San Jose Permit Extension**: 3-month extension granted (until early October 2025) for submission of additional technical/metallurgical work related to Mining Licence Application.  
- **Due Diligence Ongoing**: Continues on gold-copper projects under option from Dart Mining.  

*(Note: No material capital markets/trading impacts identified beyond operational delays and permitting updates.)*
